comment: Exactly 60 minutes from start of boil to end of cleanup.  Pitched slightly warm @ 78, put in temp controlled cooler @ 64.

Just bottled this on 6/26.  Slow ramp up with this yeast, but rockin' @ 36 hours and 64 degrees.  Hit terminal gravity in 7-8 days and nailed the predicted 1.013 FG.  Bottled with some conditioning tabs I had around (4 per 12 oz bottle).  I always batch prime so we'll see how these work.
